      "text": "He reported the incident to Leonard H.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Stringfield, 7017 Britton Avenue, Madison",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Place, director of civilian research, interplane-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "tary flying objects. He said the current reports",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "\"seem to indicate a pattern\" in the flight of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
